# Afkar Child Theme

## Description
This is the child theme for the Afkar WordPress theme. It allows you to customize the parent theme without losing the ability to update it.

## Installation
1. Download the child theme folder (`afkar-child`).
2. Upload the `afkar-child` folder to the `/wp-content/themes/` directory of your WordPress installation.
3. Go to the WordPress admin dashboard.
4. Navigate to Appearance > Themes.
5. Activate the Afkar Child theme.

## Usage
You can add custom styles to the `style.css` file of the child theme. Any modifications to the functionality of the parent theme can be added in the `functions.php` file.

## Important Notes
- Always ensure that the parent theme (Afkar) is installed and activated.
- When updating the parent theme, your customizations in the child theme will remain intact.